## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on the importance of critical reading and writing skills. Additionally, the search was limited to English-language sources, which may exclude insights from non-English-speaking regions. Further research could explore the application of these skills in diverse cultural and educational contexts.